Scope of GenAI Use: AI did not contribute to any of the ideas or creative direction; it simply wrote my ideas in code. 

Limitations or Misfires: There were times when the AI needed to be redirected to fit my vision, and as I said before, I did get an error once while using the code; however, after proper reworking, a conclusion was able to be reached. 
